# Mirrors the ALMS3 .dockerignore baseline.
# Critical entries: `**/bin`, `**/obj`. Without them, Windows-build artifacts
# (project.assets.json with C:\... fallback paths) leak into the Linux
# container and `dotnet publish` fails with
# `Unable to find fallback package folder 'C:\Program Files (x86)\...'`.

**/bin
**/obj

# IDE state
**/.vs
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/*.user
**/*.suo

# VCS / Docker / repo hygiene
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.dockerignore
**/Dockerfile*

# Test bin trees, NuGet & build caches
**/TestResults
**/.cache
**/node_modules

# Service-local extras not needed by the build
helm/
.env.local
.env.local.example
